    "Description": "This is a kernel live patch module which can be loaded by the kpatch command line utility to modify the code of a running kernel.  This patch module is targeted for kernel-5.14.0-284.52.1.el9_2.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* kernel: mptcp: cope racing subflow creation in mptcp_rcv_space_adjust (CVE-2024-53122)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
